name: Agrinam Acquisition Corporation Rights
longDescription: Agrinam Acquisition Corp is a special purpose acquisition corporation incorporated for the purpose of effecting an acquisition of one or more businesses or assets, by way of a merger, amalgamation, arrangement, share exchange, asset acquisition, share purchase, reorganization, or any other similar business combination involving the Corporation.
